T02TD3673E:286a-1: s'i ta t'a r'a s'a dha nam /
T02TD3673E:286a-3: sgrol ma dkar mo'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD3673E:286a-4: 'phags ma sgrol ma dkar mo la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3673E:286a-5: ched du zla ba drug gi bar //
T02TD3673E:286b-2: 'chi ba'i skyon gyis mi gos so //
T02TD3673E:286b-3: ngag gi dbang phyug gnang byas pa //
T02TD3673E:286b-4: 'chi bdag slu ba bsdus pa las //
T02TD3673E:286b-5: phyung nas sgrol ma dkar mo ni //
T02TD3673E:286b-6: bsgoms na 'jigs pa nyams byed pa //
T02TD3673E:286b-7: bzhi pa'i sde tshan dang po aa //
T02TD3673E:286b-9: pad dkar zla ba'i gdan bltas la //
T02TD3673E:286b-10: gsum la skyabs 'gro yang brjod la //
T02TD3673E:286b-11: rang bzhin sgro btags gzhom phyir du //
T02TD3673E:286b-12: skad cig stong pa nyid du blta //
T02TD3673E:286b-13: de nas sngon gyi smon lam dbang //
T02TD3673E:286b-14: byang chub sems kyi yi ge bsgom //
T02TD3673E:286b-15: padma dkar po'i dbus gnas pa'i //
T02TD3673E:286b-16: zla ba'i gdan gyi steng du ni //
T02TD3673E:286b-17: rdo rje skyil mo krung bcas ma //
T02TD3673E:286b-18: mchog sbyin pa dang autpa la bsnams //
T02TD3673E:286b-19: ston ka'i zla ba'i 'od gnas can //
T02TD3673E:286b-20: zla ba la ni rgyab rten cing //
T02TD3673E:286b-21: rgyan rnams thams cad rab tu rdzogs //
T02TD3673E:286b-22: bcu drug lo lon lus can ma //
T02TD3673E:286b-23: sangs rgyas kun dang de sras kyi //
T02TD3673E:286b-24: yum ni 'dod pa'i gzugs can ma //
T02TD3673E:286b-25: sgrol ma de yi thugs kar bsgom //
T02TD3673E:286b-27: re'u mig brgyad la yi ge brgyad //
T02TD3673E:286b-28: yongs su bskor bar bya ba'o //
T02TD3673E:286b-29: aom h'a gsal byed dbus gnas pa'i //
T02TD3673E:286b-30: bsgrub bya'i ming ni lte bar bya //
T02TD3673E:286b-31: zla drug rtse gcig pa yi yid //
T02TD3673E:286b-32: nges par brtan pa rtag tu bya //
T02TD3673E:286b-33: yi ge bcu pa'i sngags 'di ni //
T02TD3673E:286b-34: mi skyo'i yid kyis bzlas bya ste //
T02TD3673E:286b-35: aom gyi yi ge dang por sbyin //
T02TD3673E:286b-36: phyis ni t'a re rab tu sbyar //
T02TD3673E:286b-37: tutt'a re la tu re phyis //
T02TD3673E:286b-38: sv'a h'a mtha' ru las kun byed //
T02TD3673E:286b-39: tshangs dbang khyab 'jug nyi zla dang //
T02TD3673E:286b-40: drag po phyogs skyong 'dod lhas kyang //
T02TD3673E:286b-41: ba spu'i rtse mo'ang gcod mi nus //
T02TD3673E:286b-42: 'chi bdag las rgyal sgrol ma bzhin //
T02TD3673E:286b-43: skra dkar gnyer ma skal ngan nad //
T02TD3673E:286b-44: dbul pa la sogs mdor bsdu na //
T02TD3673E:286b-45: seng sogs 'jigs pa chen po brgyad //
T02TD3673E:286b-46: sdug bsngal rab tu 'joms byed cing //
T02TD3673E:286b-47: bskul ba med par gos btung ba //
T02TD3673E:286b-48: khang bzangs rin chen tshogs kyang 'du ;
T02TD3673E:286b-49: / ral gri dang ni mig sman dang //
T02TD3673E:286b-50: rkang pa bum pa bzang sogs 'grub //
T02TD3673E:286b-51: tshigs bcad mkhan dang ngag snyan dang //
T02TD3673E:286b-52: blo rno shes rab dri med 'gyur //
T02TD3673E:286b-53: gzhan yang ci 'dod dngos grub ni //
T02TD3673E:286b-55: sgrol ma dkar mo'i sgrub pa'i thabs //
T02TD3673E:287a-2: / gang zhig phyung nas dge bsags pa //
T02TD3673E:287a-3: des ni skye 'gro sgrol mar shog / sgrol ma dkar mo sgrub pa'i thabs //
T02TD3673E:287a-4: slob dpon ngag gi dbang phyug grags pa'i slob ma thu bos mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD3673E:287a-6: // / pandi ta don yod rdo rje dang /
T02TD3673E:287a-7: lo ts'a ba khams pa dge slong ba ris bsgyur ba'o//
